[3586.15985, "o", "\r\u001b[1mSelect model for Claude Code:\u001b[0m \u001b[3;38;5;246mType to filter...\u001b[0m                                                              \u001b[K\r\n                                                                                                             \u001b[K\r\n  \u001b[1;38;5;249mRecommended\u001b[0m                                                                                                \u001b[K\r\n    glm-5.2:cloud                                                                                            \u001b[K\r\n      \u001b[38;5;246mLong-horizon coding and agentic engineering with a solid 1M context\u001b[0m                                    \u001b[K\r\n    kimi-k2.7-code:cloud                                                                                     \u001b[K\r\n      \u001b[38;5;246mCoding-focused long-horizon agentic workflows with improved token efficiency and vision\u001b[0m                \u001b[K\r\n    minimax-m3:cloud                                                                                         \u001b[K\r\n      \u001b[38;5;246mState-of-the-art coding & agent capabilities with multimodal reasoning and support for up to 1M context\u001b[0m\u001b[K\r\n    nemotron-3-super:cloud                                                                                   \u001b[K\r\n      \u001b[38;5;246mReasoning, coding, and agentic tool use\u001b[0m                                                                \u001b[K\r\n    gemma4:12b                                                                                               \u001b[K\r\n      \u001b[38;5;246mAgentic workflows and multimodal reasoning, ~12GB, (not downloaded)\u001b[0m                                    \u001b[K\r\n    qwen3.6                                                                                                  \u001b[K\r\n      \u001b[38;5;246mAgentic software engineering model with multimodal capabilities\u001b[0m                                        \u001b[K\r\n                                                                                                             \u001b[K\r\n  \u001b[1;38;5;249mMore\u001b[0m                                                                                                       \u001b[K\r\n    bge-m3                                                                                                   \u001b[K\r\n    gemma3:4b                                                                                                \u001b[K\r\n\u001b[48;5;236m  \u001b[0m\u001b[1;48;5;236m▸ gemma4\u001b[0m                                                                                                   \u001b[K\r\n    mistral-medium-3.5                                                                                       \u001b[K\r\n      \u001b[3;38;5;246m... and 4 more\u001b[0m                                                                                         \u001b[K\r\n                                                                                                             \u001b[K\r\n\u001b[38;5;244m↑/↓ navigate • enter select • ← back\u001b[0m                                                                         \u001b[K\r"]
