opul de demo, warm TTFT ~1776ms.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5G\u001b[1m#9\u001b[8G\u001b[22m—\u001b[10Glegat\u001b[16Gtangențial:\u001b[28Gcontext\u001b[36Ghardware\u001b[45Glocal-LLM\u001b[55G(eGPU/TB4,\u001b[66GVRAM,\u001b[72GOllama)\u001b[80Gpentru\u001b[87Gacelași\u001b[95GDell\u001b[100GLatitude.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mIrrelevant (noise TF-IDF)\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[K\r\u001b[4C\u001b[1B#2, #3, #5, #7, #8 — toate Flink \"LOAD statements\", prin coincidență \u001b[75Gexicală pe \"load\". Fără legătură cu\u001b[111Ggemma.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B-\u001b[5G#4\u001b[8G—\u001b[10G\"cold-start\"\u001b[23Gîn\u001b[26Gcontext\u001b[34GFlink/k8s,\u001b[45Gnu\u001b[48GOllama.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B- #6 — port Copilot, match\u001b[30Gpe\u001b[33G\"load-bearing\".\r\u001b[2C\u001b[2BNotă:\u001b[9Gcăutarea e TF-IDF (vector search încă down), de\u001b[57Gaceea apar și Flink \"LOAD\" ca n\u001b[89Gise pe token-ul \"load\". Match-ul\u001b[122G#1\u001b[125Ge\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Btotuși\u001b[10Gclar dominant (70 vs 16).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m✻\u001b[3GCrunched for 30s\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[48;2;55;55;55m\u001b[38;2;80;80;80m❯ \u001b[38;2;255;255;255mcaută semantic: \"cât durează să pornească un model local mic?\"\u001b[39m                                                                 \r\u001b[2B\u001b[49m\u001b[38;2;215;119;87m✶\u001b[3GWrangling… \u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[3B\u001b[38;2;153;153;153m❯ \u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[45;1H\u001b[42;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
